What is a User?

A User is a person who can log in to Odoo and perform business operations based on the permissions assigned to them.

Examples:

Administrator
Sales Manager
Salesperson
Accountant
Inventory Manager
HR Officer

Each user has a unique login account.

User Information

Each user profile contains important information.

Examples:

Name
Email Address
Login Username
Password
Company
Language
Time Zone
User Photo
Job Position

This information helps identify users and personalize their Odoo experience.

